          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript is used for contemplation and recitation and is a late Vedic work, a philosophical treatise that reinterprets the symbolic value of Hindu rites and rituals, pointing to an underlying continuum between the individual self (ātman) and the universe (brahman).</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
            <msItem>
              <title>Br̥hadāraṇyakopaniṣad.</title>
